description: Taking the favorite American classic, and heaping on some mighty tasty gourmet toppings, The Mean Weenie really means business when it comes to flavor, quality, and providing Detroit with top-dop hot dogs. A few of the mean weenies you’ll wanna eat include the Keen Weenie (with sharp cheddar, apple cider braised leeks, and bourbon mustard), the Piggly Wiggly (with ultra-yummy mac & cheese, and luscious BBQ pulled pork), Guacin’ the Dog (with chipotle cheddar, homemade creamy Guacamole, and nacho cheese Dorito crumbles), and many more. So if you’ve got some mean cravings for mouthwatering handheld cuisine, this big orange truck will match your mood with its aggressively delicious food.
name: The Mean Weenie
